youth in oregon is a 2016 american comedy-drama film directed by joel david moore .   the film stars frank langella , billy crudup , christina applegate , nicola peltz , mary kay place , and josh lucas .   the film had its world premiere at the tribeca film festival on april 16 , 2016 .   the film was released in theaters on february 3 , 2017 , by orion pictures and samuel goldwyn films .